      "abstract": ") of 0.99 and 0.98, indicating excellent piecewise linear response characteristics. The response and recovery times of the sensor were 125 and 20 ms, respectively, indicating that the sensor had good fast-response characteristics. In addition, a dynamic response test of the sensor at different frequencies showed that the sensor exhibited an excellent pressure-sensitive dynamic response performance. After more than 5000 repeated loading/unloading cycles, the sensor exhibited negligible signal degradation and no observable baseline drift, demonstrating excellent durability and operational stability. The advantages of the flexible pressure sensor in wide range, high sensitivity and good durability characteristics make it have important application prospect and value in the fields of wearable devices, medical detection, robot technology and so on.",
