      "title": "Wearable High‐Performance Supercapacitors Based on Silver‐Sputtered Textiles with FeCo<sub>2</sub>S<sub>4</sub>–NiCo<sub>2</sub>S<sub>4</sub> Composite Nanotube‐Built Multitripod Architectures as Advanced Flexible Electrodes",
